INSERT INTO `general_forums` VALUES (1,28,'Mark Joseph Miranda','My COACH Experience: Conquering the IT Learning Curve','<p>Let\'s talk <b>COACH</b>! </p><p><br></p><p>Before the program, I was struggling with <b class=\"\">structuring my learning path in Information Technology</b>. I felt overwhelmed by the sheer volume of conceptsfrom cloud essentials to network securityand I couldn\'t figure out where to focus my energy. Working with my <b>mentor</b> was the key to unlocking real progress. They didn\'t just give me answers; they taught me how to find them myself by building a personalized curriculum and showing me how to break down complex technical topics into manageable study blocks.</p><p><br></p><p>Now, because of the skills and confidence I gained, I\'m <b>actively studying for my first major IT certification, speaking confidently about core networking principles, and I\'ve even started applying for roles in the field!</b></p><p><br></p><p><b>For those thinking about joining COACH:</b> It\'s 100% worth the investment. Find a mentor you can be truly open withit makes all the difference!</p><p><br></p><p><b>Share your story! What\'s one piece of advice your COACH mentor gave you that you still use today?</b></p><p><b>#COACHSuccess #MenteeLife #CareerDevelopment #SkillBuilding</b></p>','2025-10-05 07:30:48',0,'forum',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'../uploads/profile_markmrnd_1757861069.png'),(2,2,'Cherwen Kirk Fuertes','User commented','This is an amazing transformation! I totally relate to that feeling of being paralyzed by the sheer volume of IT topics. It\'s like drinking from a firehose! ','2025-10-05 07:34:11',0,'comment',1,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'../uploads/profile_ckmfuertes_1747555295.jpg'),(3,3,'Faith Odessa Balajo','Beyond the Code','<p>When you\'re learning IT, its all about the technical skills, right? Wrong! </p><p><br></p><p>One of the most valuable lessons I learned through <b>COACH</b> wasn\'t a piece of code or a networking protocol. It was the <b>soft skills</b> and <b>industry perspective</b> my mentor shared.</p><p><br></p><p>They helped me understand:</p><p><ol><li><b>How to talk to non-technical people</b> about complex IT problems.</li><li><b>Which roles are actually growing</b> in the next 5 years (not just the trendy ones).</li><li><b>How to interview</b> for an IT position when I didn\'t have years of experience.<br><br></li></ol></p><p>My mentor helped me realize that being successful in tech is 50% technical knowledge and 50% communication.</p><p><br></p><p>What\'s the best non-technical skill your mentor helped you develop?</p><p><b>#COACHMentor #SoftSkillsForTech #ITInsights #BeyondTheCode</b></p>','2025-10-05 07:36:03',0,'forum',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'../uploads/profile_fobalajo_1747553068.jpg'),(4,2,'Cherwen Kirk Fuertes','COACH Platform: Intuitive Design Makes Learning IT Easier','<p>Just logged into the <b>COACH</b> platform and I have to give a huge compliment to the design team! </p><p><br></p><p>The look of the interfacefrom the clean navigation at the top (About Us, Courses, Mentors) to the central message, \"<b>Online Learning: Connecting Aspiring Tech Learners with Expert Coaches</b>\"makes it feel immediately intuitive and focused.</p><p><br></p><p>I especially love how the design (like the coding snippets in the background and the 3D icons) makes the learning process feel both <b>high-tech and friendly</b>. When you\'re tackling complex subjects like IT, having a <b>TRUSTED</b> platform that\'s easy to navigate makes all the difference. It shows they truly prioritize the learner\'s experience.</p><p><br></p><p><b>My takeaway:</b> A great learning platform provides both expert content and an excellent user interface. COACH nails both! </p><p><br></p><p>What\'s your favorite feature of the COACH interface or course portal?</p><p><b>#COACHPlatform #UILove #OnlineLearning #TechEducation #UXDesign #Mentorship</b></p>','2025-10-05 07:39:19',0,'forum',NULL,'../uploads/forum_images/68e220a7dac16_Screenshot 2025-10-05 153725.png','68e220a7dac16_Screenshot 2025-10-05 153725.png',0,NULL,'../uploads/profile_ckmfuertes_1747555295.jpg'),(5,28,'Mark Joseph Miranda','User commented','So true! For me, it was learning how to give confident, concise updates in meetings. My mentor helped me trim five minutes of rambling into 60 seconds of impact. It really changes how senior management perceives your competence. Great post! ','2025-10-05 07:40:34',0,'comment',3,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'../uploads/profile_markmrnd_1757861069.png'),(7,28,'Mark Joseph Miranda','User commented','YES! Love that high-tech feel. The coding snippets and 3D icons make the platform feel instantly authentic and professional. It definitely helps make those complex IT topics less intimidating! Great design.  ','2025-10-05 07:42:29',0,'comment',4,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'../uploads/profile_markmrnd_1757861069.png'),(8,2,'Cherwen Kirk Fuertes','User commented','That\'s the ultimate mentorship value! The most vital non-technical skill I gained was strategic networking.','2025-10-05 07:43:36',0,'comment',3,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'../uploads/profile_ckmfuertes_1747555295.jpg'),(9,3,'Faith Odessa Balajo','User commented','','2025-10-05 07:44:35',0,'comment',4,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'../uploads/profile_fobalajo_1747553068.jpg'),(10,90,'Maine Aldub','User commented','I don\'t like the design. It\'s ugly, I don\'t agree with your opinion.','2025-10-05 07:48:04',0,'comment',4,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'img/default-user.png'),(12,90,'Maine Aldub','LOL NOT GOOD !!!','<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">I saw the post complimenting the COACH platform design, and I have to respectfully disagree. </p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Honestly, I don\'t like the design. It\'s ugly, and the interface feels cluttered. I don\'t agree with&nbsp;the opinion that it\'s \"<b>intuitive.</b>\" I find the mix of purple branding and all the random coding snippets distracting. When I\'m trying to focus on complex IT concepts, I need a clean, simple layout, not something that looks busy.</p>','2025-10-05 07:49:44',0,'forum',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'img/default-user.png'),(13,64,'Jana  Francisco','The Turning Point in My Learning Journey ','<p>We all hit walls when trying to learn something new. For me, IT felt like an endless maze with no exit. Every topic I touched led to three more I didnt understand, and I was losing motivation.<br><br></p>\r\n<p>COACH became my turning point. My mentor gave me clarity, direction, and encouragement right when I needed it. Instead of seeing IT as a mountain too high to climb, I began to see it as a pathone I could walk step by step.</p>\r\n<p>That change in perspective made all the difference. Today, Im not stuck anymoreIm moving forward with purpose, preparing for certifications, and building a career Im truly excited about.<br><br></p>\r\n<p>If youve been searching for that push to keep going, COACH might be it. Sometimes, the right mentor is all it takes to turn frustration into progress.<br><br></p>\r\n<p><b>#TurningPoint #COACHExperience #LearningJourney #CareerSuccess</b></p>','2025-10-05 10:00:55',0,'forum',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'../uploads/profile_jnfrancisco_1759658077.jpg'),(14,1,'Mark Justie Lagnason','User commented','#Success !!','2025-10-06 07:38:27',0,'comment',13,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'../uploads/profile_mjslagnason_1747550363.jpg'),(16,26,'Angela Marie Gabriel','User commented','Nice, Jana!','2025-10-07 05:29:33',0,'comment',13,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'../uploads/profile_jelaii_k_1757908035.jpg');
